Struct OqsKem

Namespace
OpenForge.Cryptography.LibOqs.KEM
Assembly
OpenForge.Cryptography.LibOqs.KEM.dll

Native structure representing LibOQS KEM algorithm information and function pointers. This structure mirrors the OQS_KEM struct from the LibOQS C library.
